{"tid":1538541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日嘅新聞我咩都聽唔到","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:28:47.000Z","uid":80985,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1eeb7d7e93b492ed7744bd3538a1dcc468842db2","tid":1538541,"uid":80985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:14:43.000Z","msg":"我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下面自己留言<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7b7bc714826d291bcdc49fe44bec817a0cf17d81","tid":1538541,"uid":80985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:18:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af604d138736aabca21bf43f03bfd0313cc92c6","tid":1538541,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:18:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤回送中法案就係要分化我地呀！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家要堅持<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n響呢個時候，大家更應該重溫一下我地O既五大訴求<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvEtnXk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvEtnXk.png&h=4b7e40e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重溫下71 立會宣言</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4lJ6vzXDEkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4lJ6vzXDEkg&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq8emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=0fa92edd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4lJ6vzXDEkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重溫721 中聯辦外宣言</span></span><br />\n（現場宣讀之版本） 721 [中聯辦]宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1338129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1338129</a><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n 721 [中聯辦]宣言<br />\n<br />\n各位香港人及世界各地關心香港的朋友：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群來自香港的示威者。由六月初至今，數以百萬計香港人多次以和平、非暴力、理性的方式，包括遊行、集會等，向政府以至全世界表達我們「反送中」的訴求。有抗爭者甚至甘願冒性命危險，背水一戰，一度進佔立法會；而短短月餘之間更加有五位手足不惜捨生取義，以死相諫，試圖喚醒香港僅餘的良知及香港人的惻隱之心。可惜，一切血汗付諸流水，只換來香港的冷漠和漠視，以及堅拒撤回回應我們。更甚者，在每次示威集會期間，政府均以前線警員為擋箭牌，放任警員濫用武力對付示威者，令大量市民受傷流血。與此同時，特首、高官以及一眾建制派議員卻拒絕回應群眾，妄圖以暴力手段解決政治問題，堅持與民為敵。<br />\n<br />\n今天，我們再一次重申對特區政府表達我們的五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例的修訂，以至法理上終止條例程序<br />\n二、收回612暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷對之前及今後所有反送中抗爭者控罪 <br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警察濫權<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行真正的雙普選<br />\n<br />\n我們熱愛香港，不願再有香港人為守護家園而流血，甚至犠牲我們寶貴的性命。但我們我們誓必以一切方法逼使政府完全回應我們的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n最後，主權移交之後，源於制度不公及制度暴力，香港政府多次推行惡法，未有循香港人的利益發展。就此我們將不排除成為臨時立法會，撥亂反正，使我們香港重回正軌，成為團結、民主、自由、公義的社會。 <br />\n---------------------------------------------------<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq8emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=b96cf6ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家要加油，要堅持，唔好咁易收貨，唔好咁易放棄<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求  缺一不可<br />\n光復香港  時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"e708dcb8c6ce3a999ff16188dee42af8812edb55","tid":1538541,"uid":80985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b67c401fb8ac1c95863fd7f624f8fad15548d25","tid":1538541,"uid":80985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:26:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6f52e2a09905259fe1a1b07309b9678b21f462","tid":1538541,"uid":80985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:28:47.000Z","msg":"我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}